Cobhams Asuquo ft. Simi | Image: Youtube Nigerian producer and singer-songwriter Cobhams Asuquo has released the music video to his song “We Plenti” featuring Simi. “We Plenti” is an inspirational song that encourages the listener to not to give up but keep working and hustling. With lyrics like “So my brother hustle, So my sister work no condition lasts forever” and “See this life na turn by turn, Your time dey come” Cobhams and Simi assures their listeners that someday their situation would get better. Watch the music video of “We Plenti” below: